OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fincreasing overnight and thickening
OL,7,Flater. Most parts staying dry,
OL,8,Falthough a few light coastal showers
OL,9,Fpossible later. Winds also gradually
OL,10,Fstrengthening, and turning gusty by
OL,11,Fdawn. Likely staying frost free.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA cloudy but mostly dry
OL,14,Fstart, but some outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fpossible by midday. These turning more
OL,16,Fpersistent through the afternoon and
OL,17,Fevening, with heavy rain arriving
OL,18,Fovernight. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
