OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold and
OL,6,Fbreezy Friday with brighter spells and
OL,7,Foccasional showers. Less cold
OL,8,FSaturday, but still the odd shower
OL,9,Flikely. Further rain and strong winds
OL,10,Fspreading east Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
